===Etymology===
{{L.}} ''[[virgo]]'', "maiden, young woman"

===Proper noun===
'''Virgo'''

#{{constellation}}: A [[constellation]] of stars supposedly shaped like a [[virgin]]. It contains the bright [[binary]] star [[Spica]].
#{{astrology}}: The [[Zodiac]] sign for the [[virgin]], covering August 23 - September 22.

